      "description": "xform -  - Select which transform is applied if the transform data is available from the input Alembic file.\n\n none - No transformation is applied to the geometry(s), they reside at the origin. transform - Applies the static local transformation for the selected geometry objects from the Object . transform - Applies the static world transformation of the selected geometry objects from the Object  up to their parents transformation. transform - In the case that the Alembic file includes dynamic or animated geometries the transformation is applied to the selected geometries. This option performs both local and world transformation (if available) for the given geometry.",
